OL,3,CMan jailed for causing 'alarm' with
OL,4,Cbomb hoax
OL,6,FA man who approached strangers in the
OL,7,Fstreet and told them he had a bomb has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FArmed police were called to Talbot
OL,11,FCrescent in Chesterfield last
OL,12,FSeptember when Leon Daines made the
OL,13,Fcomments.
OL,15,FHe had a device in his hand and
OL,16,Freportedly said to one person:
OL,17,F"There's C4 in this tin if you pull
OL,18,Fthe pin it will explode."
