OL,3,CMan jailed for causing 'alarm' with
OL,4,Cbomb hoax
OL,6,FWhen armed officers arrived at the
OL,7,Fscene they found him squirting a water
OL,8,Fpistol at passing vehicles.
OL,10,FDanies, 39 and of no fixed abode,
OL,11,Fadmitted causing a bomb hoax by
OL,12,Fcommunicating false information and
OL,13,Fwas jaled for four months at
OL,14,FChesterfield Magistrates' Court.
OL,16,FSergeant Josh Carter, of Chesterfield
OL,17,FSafter Neighbourhood Team, said: "This
OL,18,Fincident obviously caused alarm in the
OL,19,Fcommunity and took up a significant
OL,20,Famount of police resources, including
OL,21,Fdeploying armed officers.
